event.title: Event
event.description: Event that triggers a reset of all dynamic rigid bodies to their start position and orientation. The event must be fired on the app.

drawShapes.title: Draw Shapes
drawShapes.description: Draw representations of physics collision shapes

castShadows.title: Cast Shadows
castShadows.description: Cast shadows from physics collision shapes

cameraOffset.title: Camera Offset
cameraOffset.description: The local space offset with respect to the target entity coordinate system

lerpAmount.title: Lerp Amount
lerpAmount.description: The amount to lerp towards the target transform every frame

startEvent.title: Start Event
startEvent.description: Event that starts the VR session.

endEvent.title: End Event
endEvent.description: Event that ends the VR session.

space.title: Space
space.description: The tracking space for the VR session.

schema.name: event
schema.title: Event
schema.description: The event name that triggers this set action.

schema.name: entity
schema.title: Entity
schema.description: The entity from where the path starts. If unset, this entity is used.

schema.name: path
schema.title: Path
schema.description: The path to set when the event fires.

schema.name: value
schema.title: Value
schema.description: The value to set the property to.

availableEvent.title: Available Event
availableEvent.description: Fired when a VR session becomes available.

unavailableEvent.title: Unvailable Event
unavailableEvent.description: Fired when a VR session becomes unavailable.

startEvent.title: Start Event
startEvent.description: Fired when a VR session starts.

endEvent.title: End Event
endEvent.description: Fired when a VR session starts.

schema.name: key
schema.title: Key
schema.description: The keyboard key that will fire events

schema.name: keyDownEvent
schema.title: Key Down Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key is pressed

schema.name: keyRepeatEvent
schema.title: Key Repeat Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key registers a repeat press after the initial press

schema.name: keyUpEvent
schema.title: Key Up Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key is released

keys.title: Keys
keys.description: The set of keyboard keys that are configured to fire events
